                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9763" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1467</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">963 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">承古韵，创茶道：霸王茶姬的品牌崛起之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Inheriting the Ancient Elegance and Pioneering the Tea Way: The Ascent of the CHAGEE Brand</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王旭超，董博航，马林</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京茶姬餐饮管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">霸王茶姬；品牌定位；品牌扩张；品牌推广；品牌深化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CHAGEE; Brand Positioning; Brand Expansion; Brand Promotion; Brand Deepening</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，新茶饮行业竞争激烈。作为后来者的霸王茶姬，用时7年从区域性品牌跻身全球茶饮头部品牌，其成功模式值得深入探讨。本案例聚焦霸王茶姬，详细描述其品牌快速崛起的历程。霸王茶姬精准定位“新中式国风茶饮”，塑造差异化品牌优势，依托标准化生产体系与低成本供应网络，以西南为战略支点出发，实施“1+1+9+N”战略与空间错位战略，迅速席卷国内外市场。在品牌推广过程中，综合运用新媒体营销手段显著提升收入和用户规模。伴随着品牌成长，结合东方茶文化传承与多元消费场景构建，持续深化品牌内涵，提高品牌价值。通过对案例的剖析与研讨，有助于学生深入理解品牌定位、品牌扩张、品牌推广、品牌资产价值方面的理论知识，掌握品牌建设的方法论和策略，并培养“从消费者角度出发”的经营思维。本案例也能为其他新兴品牌的建设和管理提供启示和借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, the new tea drink industry is highly competitive. As a latecomer, CHAGEE has emerged from a regional brand to become a global tea drink head brand in seven years, and its success model is worth exploring in depth. This case focuses on CHAGEE, detailing the rapid rise of its brand. CHAGEE accurate positioning ‘new Chinese national style tea drinks’, shaping differentiated brand advantages, relying on standardized production system and low-cost supply network, with the Southwest as a strategic pivot, the implementation of the ‘1+1+9+N’ strategy and spatial mismatch strategy, and rapidly sweeping the domestic and international markets. In the process of brand promotion, the comprehensive use of new media marketing means to significantly increase revenue and user scale. Along with the growth of the brand, CHAGEE has continued to deepen the brand connotation and increase the brand value by combining the heritage of oriental tea culture and the construction of diversified consumption scenarios. Through the analysis and discussion of the case, it helps students to deeply understand the theoretical knowledge of brand positioning, brand expansion, brand promotion, brand equity value, master the methodology and strategy of brand building, and cultivate the business thinking of ‘starting from the consumer&#39;s perspective’. This case can also provide enlightenment and reference for the construction and management of other emerging brands.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《品牌管理》、《市场营销学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌定位钻石模型；品牌连锁经营理论；品牌用户增长模型(AARRR模型)；品牌资产模型(CBBE)</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
